    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine, mint condition inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly pampered and looks brand new, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
