      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six delivers a linear power band through individual throttle bodies, with the rod bearings and VANOS system proactively addressed to ensure mechanical integrity. The chassis features a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating the common fatigue points of this platform. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional tactile feedback and corner-exit traction. The exterior retains its factory-original depth with no panel variance, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key example for the purist collector.",
